# events

**Instance Property**

The events in the movie access log.

## Declaration

```swift
var events: [Any]! { get }
```

## Discussion

An ordered collection of [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPMovieAccessLogEvent] instances that represent the chronological sequence of events in the movie access log.

## Movie access log properties

- **extendedLogData**: A textual version of the web server access log for the associated movie player.
- **extendedLogDataStringEncoding**: The string encoding for the [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPMovieAccessLog/extendedLogData] property.
